{"tid":1412423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大民調：林鄭月娥評分再下滑至32.9分","createTime":"2019-08-05T06:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T06:58:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c37af1017854c62e26ca3a6b8b88f72ee39cd49","tid":1412423,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"中大亞太研究所最新民調顯示，行政長官林鄭月娥7月份表現評分，以100分為滿分，只有32.9分，較6月份的37.5分為低，反映民望進一步下跌。<br />\n<br />\n調查亦顯示，律政司司長鄭若驊評分只有24.1分，為三名司長中最低，政務司司長張建宗的評分最高，有35.4分，財政司司長陳茂波有32.3分。<br />\n<br />\n另外，調查亦發現，63%受訪者對特區政府表示不滿意，較6月份上升2.6個百分點；超過53%人對政府表示不信任，較6月份上升4.4個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n今次調查在上月19日至30日進行，以電話成功訪問了730多名市民。"},{"pid":"cc5a30f0debc88cb17d061c6d6203efdc4e3a170","tid":1412423,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"[repost]香港點算？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412038</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc15311e730fc08729993ef98e6a801b41cc7a44","tid":1412423,"uid":254371,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:37:03.000Z","msg":"點解仲未負數"},{"pid":"eb9f6a00751ff369f01e65ec603d0bb5298d282b","tid":1412423,"uid":68654,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"仲有30分，證明仲有班人無撚腦"},{"pid":"3b0620e28467066a12cef7723ac776ada1c2e40f","tid":1412423,"uid":39608,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"難以置信<br />\n竟然仲有32.9"},{"pid":"ac1ad8688e5b671d08327fdb86e1b4b2c074582a","tid":1412423,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"條狗閪就係想要負數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e904ca606c4e82e8bfac07684955cdda97399148","tid":1412423,"uid":50889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:39:06.000Z","msg":"唔俾 0 分果啲人究竟個腦係咩構造"},{"pid":"07c4f2eaaf6afc8ebd6eff999aa1102963b13533","tid